    "The results are shown in Table 9.",
    "We also report the Cohen's kappa scores, indicating the level of agreement among the annotators in the table.",
    "We observe that questions generated by ClaimDecomp are better than Program-FC as measured by their usefulness and quality of evidence retrieved.",
    "We also observe that the decompositions yielded by both the approaches cover all aspects of the claim, as observed by the completeness score.",
    "We also release the questions from claim decomposition for train, validation, and test sets of QuanTemp."
